OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day.
OL,6,FOvernight low cloud will gradually
OL,7,Fclear through the morning to leave all
OL,8,Fparts with plenty of sunshine. Warm
OL,9,Falong the west coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will remain dry. Patchy mist
OL,14,Fand low cloud in central and eastern
OL,15,Fareas.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FAny overnight mist and low
OL,18,Fcloud soon clearing to leave a dry day
OL,19,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Becoming warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
